{"tid":1682891,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"契媽契仔「安全屋」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-30T10:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:32:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a748223b18d535d78ef2b7b09a1f76c4532fe8cd","tid":1682891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191030/20796125/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796125%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3yNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=fa8bcdcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191030%2F20796125%2F&h=52272abe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191030/20796125/</a><br />\n<br />\n契媽契仔「安全屋」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191030/large/1572334207_0936.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191030%2Flarge%2F1572334207_0936.jpg&h=c20884ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今期流行「安全屋」。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的黃之鋒參選區議員，唯一未能入閘，極具針對性。傳原海怡西選舉主任馬周佩芬拒絕執行DQ任務，「因病休假」；由油尖旺民政事務專員蔡亮接手代辦，又傳受恐嚇有生命危險，得入住安全屋──「死亡恐嚇」來自何方？「若不DQ你就知死！」也有可能。在24小時全天候「保護」之下，不准病更不准請假，養兵千日用在一朝，必須作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方的安全屋是「保護證人組」設置的，在過渡時期保你活命不受任何威脅，達到某些目的、共識、結案、離境&hellip;&hellip;安全屋有時也不安全，甚至淪為警司帶人妻上去偷歡之幽會「炮房」，此警方桃色醜聞驚動全港。<br />\n<br />\n陪審員、污點證人、受保護人士、今日之蔡主任、殺人兇嫌陳同佳&hellip;&hellip;遲吓連林鄭也要入住安全屋了。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭被撤換，當然沒資格住禮賓府也沒警衞24小時保護，但她已是過街老鼠，邁出大門一步發生什麼事，誰可預料？她敢嗎？惟有軟禁於安全屋等待遷徙大灣區，惹起血腥風暴之送中惡法始於利用陳同佳，理應結為誼親，契媽契仔相依為命不愁寂寞，潘女（和嬰靈）亡魂會時來探訪，一眾為逆權運動慘死的亡魂也午夜敲門，一齊哭訴申冤&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"99a0e51bda14a3e0e735cea03b3c8ba4d9508a19","tid":1682891,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /Task1</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3yNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=8d88ebbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"}]}